keyValuePair.Value: Are your boys about to make history?
Are your boys about to make history?

These are certainly exciting times for the club. You've already won the %1s. A win today in the %2s would see your team complete a domestic Double. Do you feel the lads are ready to take this step into the history books?
We expect the very best.

This is a great club with a famous history. We're all about winning trophies. I hope the boys realise they can't let this opportunity pass them by. The supporters deserve this kind of success. In fact, they demand it. Let's hope the team is up to the task.
The lads will give everything.

I absolutely believe in my team. In domestic competition this season, they've shown they're out ahead of the rest. I'm very confident we can win today and do the Double. I know the lads will give everything for the club and the fans.
It's another challenge.

We've prepared well for the game and, with one trophy already in the bag, the lads are feeling pretty confident. Now it's all about being focused on the job. We have to work as hard today as we've worked all season if we are going to pull off this Double.
Double Up For %1s?

It's already been a great season for %1s, of course. The %2s trophy sits proudly in the club boardroom. Today, though, they could claim the %3s as well. They've been the dominant team over several months. This is their chance to claim glory in the shape of an historic domestic Double.
Are your boys going to do the Double?
Are your boys going to do the Double?

These are exciting times for everybody connected with the club. You've already lifted the %1s. Today you could complete a remarkable Double by adding the %2s trophy to your collection. Can you go out and enjoy it? Or are your boys feeling the pressure?
The players know what's expected of them.

The boys know they're representing a top club, a club that demands success. We've tried to develop a winning mentality and that'll be tested today. We mustn't think one trophy is enough for us. We have to finish the job by completing the Double today.
I trust my players to get the job done.

The team have been fantastic all season. I think everybody at the club can already be proud of them. But the spirit in our dressing room means we won't ever get complacent. The lads are desperate to get the job done today with a Double on the line.
We won't lose our heads.

Of course we're confident. This is a talented group of players and we work hard for each other. We've already won one trophy but I'm sure the boys aren't ready to settle for that. We've prepared well and now we're focused on claiming that Double success.
Can the team live up to expectations?
Can the team live up to expectations?

Your team have already tasted glory in the %1s. Now they have the chance to claim a second trophy in the shape of this season's %2s. Are you confident about your team's chances? Can they cope with the weight of expectation from the fans?
We've set our standards high.

Nobody who represents this club should ever be prepared to be happy with second-best. We've set our standards high and we will be focused on maintaining them today. The boys know we're here to win. Our fans and our own professional pride will make sure we don't settle for anything less.
They deserve the glory.

The team's been fantastic to work with all season. They've given everything for me, for the fans and for each other. Now, it's time for one last, big effort. We know we're good enough. We just have to go out and prove it.
I trust these players.

Of course I'm confident. This team has a great spirit and a winning mentality. If things go our way today, we'll have written a little bit of history. Whatever happens, though, I'm proud of what we've achieved together this season
%1s's Double Vision

%1s are a team standing on the brink of making history. With the %2s title already won, victory today will see them claim the %3s and, with it, a unique continental Double. Supporters are already on standby, ready to celebrate this next step to glory for their club.
%1s Look To Claim Second Trophy

They've already lifted the %2s trophy this season. Now, a second challenge lies in front of this exciting young team. They can claim the %3s title with a victory today. Excitement's been building all week. The pressure's on. Do %1s have what it takes? We're about to find out!
Treble Tops For %1s?

It feels like a date with destiny for this exciting and all-conquering %1s team. Two trophies are already in the bag: the %2s and the %3s. Today, they go into the game chasing the win which will secure the %4s and, with it, an historic Treble for this famous club.
Are your boys ready to do it?
Are your boys ready to do it?

It could be an historic day for the club. Your team has already won the %1s and the %2s. Victory today in the %3s will complete an amazing Treble and round off a memorable season. Are you feeling confident? Or is the pressure finally getting to your boys?
This club is all about trophies.

Our target at the start of every season is clear. Just competing isn't ever enough. We chase every trophy. Our intention is always to win. So far, so good. The team has done well. But all of us -- players, staff and fans -- won't feel like the job's done unless we win the game today.
The boys have been amazing.

Of course I'm confident we're going to win and complete this Treble today. But everyone should bear in mind that what the boys have already achieved is amazing. I think we've shown all season we're the best around. Now we just have to go out and prove we are, one final time.
It's just another game.

They say, in situations like this, you have to try to play the game and not the occasion. This team has a winning mentality. The boys know this game could put them in the history books. But all they're focused on is the job they have to do. If they do that, then the Treble will take care of itself, right?
%1s To Seal Domestic Domination?

%1s have swept all before them in domestic competition this season. It's no exaggeration to say they've been a class apart. The %2s and %3s winners can complete a remarkable Treble today with victory in the %4s. History is there, waiting to be made.
%1s To Lift Third Trophy?
Can your boys really pull it off?
Can your boys really pull it off?

It's already been a great season for your team. You've blown the competition away and re-written the history books at the same time. Today, your %1s and %2s winners can complete a Treble with victory in the %3s. Do you believe the boys are ready?
They're ready to give everything again.

It's the secret to every great team. Once you win a trophy, you're straight away looking to the next one. This team has that mentality. We have to go out and give everything again. The trophies we've already won mean nothing now. It's all about today.
We've been the team to beat all season.

I knew this could be a special team. But I never imagined things would come together as quickly as they have. The players deserve all the credit. Great quality, great spirit, great attitude. I hope we can go out and complete this Treble today. It's what the lads deserve.
We'll be ready, for sure.

It's all about preparation. We've won two trophies already this season but we'll go into this game as if we haven't won anything so far. We're confident but we're not complacent. The boys are ready. They know they've got a job to do.
Are your lads feeling the pressure?
Are your lads feeling the pressure?

Your team has already achieved so much this season, winning both the %1s and the %2s. Today you could complete a Treble with victory in the %3s. Is there extra pressure on your boys now? Or will this be just another game?
We're ready to go to work.

It's been a great season for everybody connected with the club. Everything we've achieved so far has been possible because of how hard the boys have been prepared to work. If we can maintain those levels of performance today then I'm confident we'll win
They're the best I've ever worked with.

I think these boys have forgotten how to lose! It's been a great experience working with this group this season. They've been so consistent, ready to give everything in every single game. If the team can put in one final effort today, then I'm pretty confident we'll run out winners.
We won't be complacent.

This team has already had so much to celebrate this season. But I don't see the boys having lost their edge at all. They're confident but they won't be complacent. They want this Treble now. For the club, for the supporters and for themselves.
Four Up For %1s?

They've made headlines all season with sensational victories, scintillating performances and triumphs in the %2s, the %3s and the %4s. Today, though, could be a special day even by %1s's own high standards: victory will see them lift the %5s and complete an unprecedented Quadruple.
Do you think the Quadruple's possible now?
Do you think the Quadruple's possible now?

Today could turn out to be the climax to what's already been an amazing season. Your team's already lifted the %1s, %2s and %3s trophies, victory today and the boys would claim the %4s and an historic Quadruple. Do you think we're going to see history being made?
It's up to the players.

Of course this is an incredible opportunity. The kind that comes along once in a career, if you're lucky. Four trophies in a season? Amazing. So I've just asked the boys: how much do you want this? They'll give us an answer to that question later, won't they?
Anything's possible for this team.

This team's incredible. Every question they've been asked all season, they've come up with an answer. Without a doubt, we're the best team around at the moment. I'll never work with a group of players as good as these lads ever again, that's for sure. I can't see us losing today!
That's a question for the boys to answer.

What we've already achieved is beyond anything we could have imagined. Winning today would just make the season perfect. This team is so strong mentally, I'm pretty sure they'll come up with a way to win this game just like they have so many times this season. Let's just wait and see.
Four Up For %1s?

They've made headlines all season with sensational victories, scintillating performances and triumphs in the %2s, the %3s and the %4s. Today, though, could be a special day even by %1s's own high standards: victory will see them lift the %5s and complete an unprecedented Quadruple.
Can this season get even better?
Can this season get even better?

It's just got better and better for your team as the season's gone on, hasn't it? Already Treble winners: %1s, %2s and %3s. And today you're chasing the %4s and a Quadruple. Can your boys pull off the impossible and win the lot? What's the mood like in the dressing room?
This is a very determined team.

Look, I think the boys know how close they are to achieving something historic, something unprecedented. Three trophies is incredible, but I don't think this team will be satisfied with that. They'll be desperate to win today. Would you bet against them?
This team's got everything.

This is a team unlike any I've ever worked with. They've got everything: technical quality, athleticism, intelligence, desire. At the moment, I'm backing them to win every time they play. Four trophies in a season? Why not? This team has forgotten how to lose! They're untouchable.
I'm proud of them.

The team's been fantastic all season. They've lifted themselves game after game. Every player's put in a 9 out of 10, week after week. They're so close to something truly unforgettable here. I don't think they'll be taking anything for granted today. Three trophies? Incredible! Four? Just wait and see.
